(44, 19, 27, 36, 2, 11, 11, 'whom all Asia and the world worshippeth', 'Worship of False Gods', 'This connection highlights the theme of the worship of false gods, as seen in both passages. Acts 19:27 mentions the worship of Diana, while Zephaniah 2:11 speaks of the Lord''s power over all gods of the earth.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
