(44, 19, 29, 57, 1, 24, 24, 'Aristarchus', 'Connection through Aristarchus', 'Both passages emphasize Aristarchus as a companion of Paul. In Acts, he is mentioned during a tumultuous event, while in Philemon, he is recognized as a fellow laborer.', 'keyword', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
