(44, 19, 30, 10, 21, 17, 17, 'suffered him not', 'Protection of Key Figures', 'This connection highlights the theme of protection for key figures in both passages. In Acts, Paul''s disciples prevent him from entering danger, while in 2 Samuel, Abishai protects David from further battle.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
